Better Luck Tomorrow;;79;;81;;R;;An accomplished high school student, Ben (Parry Shen) seems to excel at almost everything except winning over his dream girl, Stephanie (Karin Anna Cheung). When he begins an unlikely friendship with trouble-seeking tough guy Daric (Roger Fan), Ben becomes involved in petty crime that gets increasingly dangerous, with his various illegal ventures extending to include Stephanie and her wealthy beau, Steve (John Cho). Can these restless teens curb their criminal activities before it's too late?;;Crime,Drama;;Justin Lin;;2002;;Parry Shen,Jason Tobin,Sung Kang,Roger Fan,John Cho,Karin Anna Cheung,Jerry Mathers;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/better_luck_tomorrow